1. Iterate over the string and count the capital characters.
2. Return True if:-
	a. Count of Capital Characters is equal to the length of String => **All Capital (1st Condition)**
	b. Count of Capital Characters if 0 => **All Small (2nd Condition)**
	c. Count of Capital is 1 and the Capital Character is on 0th index => **Only first letter Capital (3rd Condition)**
3. Return False otherwise

